channel.title: Help! List of commands (ALL)
channel.description:
Does anyone know a good list of commands for admin, mod, owner? I tried goolge but, just a bunch of spam of 'How to start your own server'. I am using AllStar v2 and wondering what are the comamnds for that and if you can, can you please share some 'outside' source comamnds
thank you

item.title: Help! List of commands (ALL)
item.dc:creator: @ztr_zac1 ztr zac
item.description:
@ztr_zac1 wrote:

Servers each contain different commands. If you want extra commands, make them. Its basic. There is not really an accurate command list anymore as servers has developed from the basic commands that mopar started with. Cant help you any more. If you need creating commands i no theres a tutorial in the server tutorials section.
